data.description: Nestled in the front of the neighborhood in a cul-de-sac, this magnificent 5 bedroom 3.5 bathroom home offers 2852 square feet of living experience. Upon entering you are greeted by a large living space and or can be used as a dining room or flex space. The primary bedroom is conveniently located on the first floor while the secondary bedrooms are located on the second floor. The primary bathroom offers a double vanity, garden tub, separate walk in shower and a large walk in closet. The heart of the home is the open concept kitchen and living room, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet moments by the fireplace. Upstairs you will find the rest of the generously sized bedrooms along with a game room. The backyard is a verdant oasis that offers endless opportunities for outdoor activities, from summer barbecues on the patio to children's playtime or even gardening projects. With it's perfect blend of spacious interior and vast, inviting backyard this home promises a comfortable lifestyle.   Seller is contributing $5,000 towards buyers closing costs!
